<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>تكبيرات العيد</title>

<style>

body{
background:#0f172a;
color:white;
font-family:sans-serif;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
height:100vh;
margin:0;
}

.card{
width:90%;
max-width:400px;
background:#1e293b;
padding:30px;
border-radius:20px;
text-align:center;
}

h1{
font-size:40px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

button{
background:#22c55e;
border:none;
padding:15px 25px;
border-radius:12px;
font-size:20px;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:20px;
}

audio{
width:100%;
margin-top:20px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<h1>🕌 تكبيرات العيد</h1>

<p>
استمع وانشر الأجر بإذن الله
</p>

<audio controls loop>
<source src="takbirat.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

</div>

</body>
</html>
